  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK727">
<l>pakaiyakattup pēṭikai yoḷvā ḷavaiyakat</l>
<l>tañcu mavaṉkaṟṟa nūl</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The learning of him who is diffident before an assembly is like the shining sword of an hermaphrodite in the presence of his foes.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
